ality to ensure photos can be deleted from this view.\n\nNow users can access the PhotosDateGroupScreen by clicking the \&quot;View photos by date\&quot; button when looking at photos in the CoordinatesScreen. The PhotosDateGroupScreen provides three different ways to view photos: by date category, by month, or all photos together.&quot;}]}]}" />
